    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Collectively describes living beings that reside in the ocean. This term is often additionally used to describe legendary or mythological beings thought to live in oceans or seas.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
